        public final BatchDeliveryReport.Builder using(BatchDeliveryReport instance)
        Fill a builder with attribute values from the provided BatchDeliveryReport instance. Regular attribute values will be replaced with those from the given instance. Absent optional values will not replace present values. Collection elements and entries will be added, not replaced.
